1
00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:47,040
When did you start having feelings for me?

2
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:49,560
I've had my eyes on you for a while.

3
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,640
Nila.

4
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:57,680
You're like a drug.

5
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,560
You make me addicted.

6
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:02,360
I can't get enough of you.

7
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,039
Angwei.

8
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:26,520
Angwei.

9
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,240
Mr. Danpa is here.

10
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:33,960
Mr. Danpa.

11
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:34,960
Mr. Danpa.

12
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,000
Good evening, everyone.

13
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,120
Today's charity dinner

14
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,039
is mainly focused on

15
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:44,039
orphaned children in recent years,

16
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:47,240
addressing their growth and educational issues.

17
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,680
Now, I will explain the details

18
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,479
to everyone.

19
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:52,000
I knew you would come.

20
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,400
It was hard to decline such a gracious invitation.

21
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,040
Feifei.

22
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,480
Did you forget about our contract?

23
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,640
Feifei,

24
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,020
ignore him.

25
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,079
Let's go.

26
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,280
Ou Shaowen!

27
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:22,880
Are you crazy?

28
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,440
My private secretary,

29
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:26,700
when did it become your turn to touch her?

30
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,240
Alright.

31
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:31,840
Everyone.

32
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:33,920
Next,

33
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:35,800
I want to introduce

34
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,560
my son to you all.

35
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:38,600
Angwei,

36
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,840
come meet everyone.

37
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,280
Mr. Angwei.

38
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:50,120
Mr. Angwei.

39
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,600
This is my son.

40
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,100
Please excuse him.

41
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,530
There's one more important thing.

42
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:16,400
The young master of the Ou family from Siam Group

43
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,730
is young and promising.

44
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,680
Shaowen, come here.

45
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:26,360
I have decided to hand over 30% of the pier's berths

46
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:28,360
for you to manage,

47
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:31,640
as a sign of the friendship between our two families,

48
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,970
to build a prosperous business together.

49
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,210
Thank you, Uncle Danpa.

50
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,920
Second,

51
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:46,570
the operating rights for the Leo route

52
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:50,440
will be fully handled by my son, Angwei.

53
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,320
Furthermore,

54
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,680
to ensure fairness,

55
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,920
I will set up a

56
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:01,800
supervisory committee.

57
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,560
Lapeng.

58
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,520
It will be managed by my wife, Ruannila,

59
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,200
and a few elders.

60
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,280
I'm going to the restroom.

61
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,340
Mainly to supervise the operations.

62
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,400
Angwei.

63
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:23,880
Stop.

64
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,090
Who exactly are you?

65
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,000
My name is Feifei.

66
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:39,250
Don't think changing your name

67
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,480
can fool me.

68
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:44,440
Madam, you have the wrong person.

69
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:49,120
Tell me, why does your face

70
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,840
look exactly like

71
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,040
that little bitch?

72
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,440
Little bitch?

73
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:04,280
Are you talking about Miss Dailing, Madam?

74
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:07,380
I heard her biological mother passed away long ago.

75
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:10,240
She is the stepdaughter of you and Mr. Danpa.

76
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,570
Then as her stepmother,

77
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,520
seeing a face exactly like hers,

78
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,280
aren't you happy?

79
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,880
Why should I be happy?

80
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,680
So you hate her.

81
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,800
Why should I hate her?

82
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,360
If you don't hate her,

83
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,040
why do you look

84
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,560
so afraid?

85
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:29,200
Or was there something suspicious about Miss Dai's death back then?

86
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:30,200
You did it.

87
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:33,360
Shut up.

88
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,840
How could her death have anything to do with me?

89
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,400
It was an accident.

90
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:41,280
She was just unlucky.

91
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,880
Then where did your good luck

92
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,400
come from, Madam?

93
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,000
You are Dailing.

94
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,320
I am Feifei.

95
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,159
If you are not Dailing...

96
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:58,880
How do you know so much about this?

97
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,760
One more thing.

98
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,960
Let's invite my wife, Ruannila,

99
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:06,010
to say a few words. Is that okay?

100
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:26,170
Where did you get these?

101
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,680
It doesn't matter where I got them.

102
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,140
What matters is that if these photos get out,

103
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,960
Uncle Danpa will lose face.

104
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:36,800
Ruannila will lose her position as his wife,

105
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:39,000
and the Chen family will be humiliated.

106
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,920
Ou Shaowen, Ou Shaowen.

107
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,980
It seems you still don't know me well enough.

108
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:50,440
You'd better muddy the waters as much as possible.

109
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,580
I'm here to talk about a partnership.

110
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,400
Ruannila planted a spy in Siam Group

111
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,400
and ruined three of my deals.

112
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,440
She whispers in Uncle Danpa's ear

113
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,120
to rightfully steal your inheritance.

114
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,320
And then?

115
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,520
So Ruannila is our common enemy.

116
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:16,020
I can help you take down Ruannila,

117
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,820
gain Uncle Danpa's trust,

118
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,770
and even help you secure the shipping routes.

119
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,380
I only have one condition.

120
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,640
Give Feifei to me.

121
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,280
So that's what you're after.

122
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,240
Ou Shaowen.

123
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,820
Let me tell you.

124
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:41,000
Feifei is mine.

125
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:43,480
The route is mine too.

126
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,280
If you dare to go after her again,

127
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:47,240
I wouldn't mind making your entire Siam Group

128
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,360
disappear from Mancheng.

129
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,840
You tied Feifei down with a contract

130
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,560
just because she looks like Dailing,

131
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,820
to be her replacement.

132
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,680
Dailing is dead.

133
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,840
She died five years ago.

134
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,620
The person by your side now is Feifei.

135
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:01,920
Stop deceiving yourself.

136
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,640
Shut up.

137
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,580
Ou Shaowen.

138
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,080
I warned you.

139
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:11,450
It's not your place to interfere with how I do things.

140
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,740
It's so lively down there.

141
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,440
Mr. Lapeng,

142
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,020
why are you here all alone?

143
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,520
You know me?

144
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,720
Very well.

145
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,920
Did you forget?

146
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,660
Five years ago,

147
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,860
a girl saw you with her own eyes

148
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:53,280
pour gasoline and burn her mother to death.

149
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,860
Have you forgotten me?

150
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,480
So it's you.

151
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:59,740
I didn't expect you to still be alive.

152
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,920
You've changed so much

153
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,800
that I didn't recognize you at first.

154
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,240
What are you doing?

155
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,400
Today is your last day.

156
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,000
I will avenge my mother.

157
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:36,160
Dailing.

158
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:57,680
Danpa, Angwei, Ruan Nila.

159
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,440
Lillian's daughter

160
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,840
has come for your lives.
